Man, is that a run-on sentence.<br /><br />It depends on which games you want to include, in particular how big they are and what mapper they use. If all the games use simple mappers (NROM, CNROM, UNROM/UOROM, AMROM/ANROM/AOROM, BNROM), you could use a mapper 28 cartridge with the Action 53 engine.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Wed Mar 21, 2018 12:12 pm</p><hr />
